Mauritius New Finance Minister Bunwaree Says Department to Continue Work

-- B y   K a m l e s h   B h u c k o r y
-- 
2011-07-27T13:18:50Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-27/mauritius-new-finance-minister-bunwaree-says-department-to-continue-work.html
Vasant Bunwaree, Mauritius’s
education minister who is also now finance minister, said work
in the ministry will continue according to the government’s
agenda as he takes up the position.  “I’m taking the job with the all the required
seriousness,” he said by phone today from Phoenix, south of the
capital,  Port Louis . “The next five months are the most
important, with pre-budget meetings” taking place.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Kamlesh Bhuckory in Port Louis at 
 kbhuckory@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
